        <p class="leading-relaxed">South Carolina families have access to the full range of preneed insurance carriers that serve the Southeast market. Working with an independent preneed agent &mdash; rather than a funeral-home-employed counselor &mdash; gives you access to multiple carriers and the ability to compare plans side by side. Here are the major carriers I work with in South Carolina:</p>
